                " 40 MICROMETER THICK ARAMID FOILS AS ENTRANCE AND EXIT",
                " WINDOWS. THE TARGET GAS WAS HIGH PURITY, RESEARCH",
                " GRADE HELIUM-3 GAS. THE GAS PRESSURE WAS 700-750 TORR."
              ]
